CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 7, 1956, pg. A15, reads: "Steelworkers Idled by Strike - Plants Closed Down - At the big Jones and Laughlin mill at Aliquippa, John Staton, Vester Harmon, Andy Gendek, Sonny Vranesevich, Frank Romeo, Mike Young and Steve Thomas, vice president of Local 1211, and 11,000 member union joke while sitting on the picket line outside the tunnel entrance of the plant... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Members of union Local 1211 John Staton, Vester Harmon, Andy Gendek, Sonny Vranesevich, Frank Romeo, Mike Young and Steve Thomas, picketing in front of J & L Steel, Aliquippa Works, Franklin Avenue, Aliquippa
